@startuml Login_Activity_States
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor #E1F5FE
    BorderColor #01579B
}

[*] --> Initializing : onCreate()

Initializing --> UserTypeSelection : initViews()
UserTypeSelection --> LoginForm : User Type Selected

LoginForm --> Validating : Login Button Clicked
LoginForm --> Registering : Register Button Clicked
LoginForm --> GuestMode : Guest Button Clicked
LoginForm --> UserTypeSelection : Back Button Clicked

Validating --> ValidatingInput : Validate Email/Password
ValidatingInput --> LoggingIn : Input Valid
ValidatingInput --> LoginForm : Input Invalid

LoggingIn --> LoginSuccess : Authentication Success
LoggingIn --> LoginError : Authentication Failed

LoginSuccess --> MainScreen : Navigate to MainActivity
GuestMode --> MainScreen : Navigate to MainActivity
Registering --> MainScreen : Registration Complete

LoginError --> LoginForm : Show Error Message

MainScreen --> [*] : Activity Finished

@enduml
